works.description: To celebrate the upcoming royal wedding of Prince William and Kate Middleton, London is putting on its best face. Now, a Lancashire-based ice cream maker named Colin Bleasdale has planned to mark the Royal Wedding Day by making an ice cream, which could break the record for the world’s most expensive ice cream. Colin Bleasdale is set to make a floral bouquet style ice cream, and hopes it to make an entry into the Guinness Book of Records. Mr Bleasdale said…
